This code provides an implementation of the method described in the
following publication: 

Y. Zhang, L. Ding and G. Sharma, ''Local-linear-fitting-based matting
 approach for joint hole filling and depth upsampling of RGB-D
 images,'' Journal of Electronic Imaging, 2019, accepted for
 publication, to appear.
 
